node.contents: I have a JApplet that works when run by appletviewer but not when run by Firefox or IE. It displays an empty rectangle with "Error. Click for details." Clicking on it brings up the window that says, "Application Error. RuntimeException. java.lang.reflect.InvocationTargetException."
